<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Sam Frost is used to delivering lines on the soap opera Home and Away.</p>

<p>But on Friday, she revealed the 'very confronting' mishap that happened while stripping down onstage for Channel Seven's charity show The All New Monty: Guys and Gals.</p>

<p>The 31-year-old actress told Nova's Fitzy and Wippa: 'I was absolutely terrified, I was shaking, I was very anxious.'</p>

<p>Oh dear! Home and Away's Sam Frost (pictured) revealed the 'very confronting' onstage mishap as she stripped in front of her co-stars for The All New Monty: Guys and Gals</p>

<p>'I had all my colleagues in the audience and my bosses! It was very confronting!'</p>

<p>The blonde beauty added that she and her co-performers - including the likes of Danielle Spencer and Fiona O'Loughlin - did not have a proper run through of their routine before the show.  </p>

<p>'They're like, 'oh don't worry, no one is going to see there's going to be smoke blah, blah, blah.''</p>

<p>'It was very confronting!' The 31-year-old actress told Nova's Fitzy and Wippa : 'I was absolutely terrified, I was shaking, I was very anxious. I had all my colleagues in the audience and my bosses!' Pictured left to right is Erin Holland, Danielle Spencer and Sam on the left</p>

<p>She explained that they were told that a smoke machine would provide them with enough cover while on stage - but was rather surprised when that was not the case.</p>

<p>'Then we got there and there wasn't that much smoke and I was like, 'oh this is weird!''</p>

<p>Sam will also perform in the burlesque show alongside beauty queen Erin Holland, entertainer Patti Newton and former Olympian Leisel Jones.</p>

<p>Uh oh: The blonde beauty added that she and her co-performers were told that a smoke machine would provide them with enough cover while on stage. Sam said, 'Then we got there and there wasn't that much smoke and I was like, 'oh this is weird!''</p>

<p>The ladies will be joined on stage by male celebrities, including actor Samuel Johnson, former Home and Away star Orpheus Pledger and comedian Paul Fenech.</p>

<p>The All New Monty: Guys and Gals will see 15 celebrities in total bare all to raise awareness of early detection and prevention of cancer.</p>

<p>The All New Monty: Guys and Gals continues Sunday at 7pm on Channel Seven</p>

